instructions: On your iPhone or iPad, open the Chrome app . Tap More and then New Incognito Tab . A new Incognito tab opens.
On your iPhone or iPad, open the Chrome app . At the bottom, tap Switch tabs . Swipe right or left to switch between Incognito tabs and regular Chrome tabs.
On your iPhone or iPad, open the Chrome app . At the bottom, tap Switch tabs . Swipe right to see your open Incognito tabs. Find the tab you want to close. At the top right of the tab, tap Close .
